@startuml
title BP-09 - Payment Rule and Policy Configuration

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Open payment policy configuration;
:Input code, name and description;
:Configure partial payment flag;
:Configure minimum amount and minimum percentage;
:Configure overpayment and auto close rules;

|Platform|
:Read TenantID from JWT context;
:Normalize policy fields;

if (Partial payment allowed?) then (Yes)
  :Validate minimum amount or minimum percentage is configured;
else (No)
  :Set minimum amount to zero;
  :Set minimum percentage to zero;
endif

:Validate percentage range between zero and one hundred;
:Validate code uniqueness within tenant;

if (Validation passed?) then (Yes)
  :Create or update PaymentPolicy;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Finance Officer|
:Use policy when configuring PaymentProduct;
stop

note right
Current endpoints:
- POST /payment-policies
- GET /payment-policies
- GET /payment-policies/{id}
- PUT /payment-policies/{id}
end note
@enduml
